title: #153 - MrBeast Saves The Planet & Twitch Is Collapsing
description:
On this episode of The H3 Podcast the gang debriefs on our Trisha Paytas episode, we discuss the fires burning down LA, Bobby Lee pops in for a surprise visit, Ethan's feeding window is working, MrBeast is planting trillions of trees, we taste test fast food salads, discuss Shroud destroying Twitch.tv, and a whole lot more!
  
 Here are some of the links from today's show:
 Podcast memes: https://imgur.com/a/goGFroW
 MrBeast's fundraiser: https://www.teamtrees.org/
 Some r/freefolk memes: https://imgur.com/a/rSjUuce
 Shroud's announcement video: https://twitter.com/shroud/status/1187413389582061568
